<div id="review_3292118917" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3292118917" />
    <a title="Wendy Hughes" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/113371199-wendy-hughes"><img alt="Wendy Hughes" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1587061183p2/113371199.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3292118917?book_show_action=true">Apr 20, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wendy Hughes" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wendy Hughes" href="/user/show/113371199-wendy-hughes">Wendy Hughes</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/113371199-wendy-hughes?shelf=2009">2009</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3292118917" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13893830108836209412">Volume 4 in the 6 book series of the Great and Terrible by Chris Stewart- I read The first three books a couple years ago. I read this book in one day I have enjoyed this series, I am looking forward to reading the next two books to complete the series.<br/>The way the books are written it puts life in perspective and seems that this could be a real possibility in our world. I like the way it portrays the good and evil- it’s so believable. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review3292118917">
